{
  "stem": "27409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Saturday afternoon, and often during the week, we went out for military exercise, shooting, hand grenade throwing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was active officers were training us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came always from a local regiment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- the basic instruction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had some sergeant who introduced us to Romanian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were only two of the Jewish which were in this cadet formation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was a son of a-- [INAUDIBLE] colonel in the Romanian army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in order to come outside, they were warned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were compulsorily selected, if you could call it so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the age of 18, if I remember well, 17, 18, there-- every Romanian youngster had to join the paramilitary training.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we drafted in to the cadet force, served after as training officers for our-- the same year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to train well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the summer, we had summer camps in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were sent in different-- that was the royal groups, they called it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They sent first military training in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And afterward, we were attending-- my was statistics and so on, in the villages, and the mountain to go around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was, himself, military lines educated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, be healthy and serve in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was first-- in Charlottenburg, he was taken in the German army, where he made the officer courses and was sent to the front in Bosnia, today is Bosnia, where he won, the First World War, the Iron Cross.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he was transferred to our home regiment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a 41 k.u.k.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Frontier Regiment, where he served up to the end of the war, fighting with the Russian, who was-- which invaded Bukowina.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
